    <item>
      <title>调查显示，英美资源集团收购价格需要超过每股 30 英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/anglo-american-takeover-price-needs-to-surpass-30-share-survey</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社调查的分析师和交易员称，收购英美资源集团的报价需要超过每股 30 英镑（37.6 美元），高于必和必拓集团上周提出的价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/anglo-american-takeover-price-needs-to-surpass-30-share-survey</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 09:38:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员撤离引发巨幅波动，可可暴跌创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/cocoa-slumps-26-in-two-days-paring-back-historic-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[可可价格出现史上最大跌幅 — — 仅两天就暴跌 27% — — 由于越来越少的投资者和公司能够维持交易头寸，价格波动变得更加剧烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/cocoa-slumps-26-in-two-days-paring-back-historic-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 09:12:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
